Q:\mathbb O\to\mathbb Q
Q\left(2n-1\right) = \left\lbrace \begin{array}{c} \prod\limits_{i=1}^{n}\left(2i-1\right),\text{    if }n > 0; \\  \prod\limits_{i=n+1}^{0}\dfrac{1}{2i-1},\text{    if }n \leq 0 \end{array} \right.
